: \"diversity\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"equity\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most coaching and leadership roles today require the coach to first understand their audience before attempting to lead them.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most coaching and leadership roles\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"their audience\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no longer effective to simply impose your culture, way, worldview or coaching philosophy onto the room - like most old school coaches and leaders did, and many still do.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your culture\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"philosophy\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The lesson for any coach or leader, is to take time to understand the people you are working with.\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lesson\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"any coach\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"leader\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not simply impose your way, personality, knowledge or personal biases on the group.\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your way\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"personality\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"personal biases\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take time to listen and observe before speaking.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The better you understand the more you can tailor your coaching approach to meet the team's needs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your coaching approach\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's needs\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He feels that growing up the South African way is of significant benefit.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the South African way\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"significant benefit\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Life in South Africa is not easy.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Life\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"South Africa\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africans know this To succeed as an entrepreneur in South Africa, a category into which sport coaching might fall, requires a can-do, thick-skinned,boer maak 'n planattitude to solving problems.\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.665099057542232e-16, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"South Africans\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"an entrepreneur\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"a category\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"sport coaching\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"boer maak\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3237}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most first-world nations have it far easier, which does not require nor teach the same levels resilience, determination, and grit to succeeded against the odds.\\\"\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most first-world nations\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"the same levels resilience\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"grit\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upton is now 55 but he has crammed a lifetime of knowledge and leadership skills into a distinguished career.\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\", \"score\": 0.9999999997471605, \"rank\": 2.5308536508218637e-10, \"text\": \"Upton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upton-by-Chester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge and leadership skills\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"a distinguished career\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He feels that South Africans should be more confident in their skillsets.\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"South Africans\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"their skillsets\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Strangely, South Africans in general tend to be unnecessarily apologetic,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"South Africans\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We suffer impostor syndrome more than the norm, and do not really believe we can be major players on the world stage.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"impostor syndrome\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3758}, {\"ngram\": \"major players\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3809}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not knowing our value works against our nation's athletes.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our value\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"our nation's athletes\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This mindset tends to see us lacking confidence and playing smaller than our talent and hard work warrants.\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This mindset\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 3936}, {\"ngram\": \"our talent\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work warrants\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also tend to give opponents from bigger or more 'high functioning' countries too much (unwarranted) respect.\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger or more 'high functioning' countries\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"too much (unwarranted) respect\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First, let us call out the elephant in the room.\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4124}, {\"ngram\": \"the elephant\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4146}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South African sport is rife with politicians and elected officials who lead with a mixture of incompetence and their o